# 🎨 Three.js Rules (MDC)

## Imports

-   ✅ **REQUIRED**: Always import individual items from three.js (named imports only, no default/namespace imports)
-   Example: `import { Scene, PerspectiveCamera, WebGLRenderer } from 'three'`

## Object Naming

-   ✅ **REQUIRED**: Always set `object.name` on all Object3D objects (Scene, Mesh, Group, Camera, etc.) immediately upon creation
-   ❌ **NO** objects in the scene without a `name` property set
-   Examples: `scene.name = 'MainScene'`, `mesh.name = 'TattooMesh'`, `camera.name = 'MainCamera'`

